<section>
    <h2>Next, it was time to hear what users wanted from the app.</h2>
    <p>The Knovel team put in touch with several users of the existing app, who we interviewed to learn more about the app fit into their workflow. The client wanted to be sure we would leave this phase of the project with a clear &ldquo;yes or no&rdquo; to each of the features we had defined previously, but I did my best to balance that with understanding more broadly what was important to each of the interviewees.</p>
